channel.title: How do I make a client work?
channel.description:
Well, first of all I can't find a client for a 508 rsps, and i don't know how to make one.
I've been using a ip changing one for other people to connect to my server.
I've had another problem, it won't let others connect. Only 3 people have been able to get on my server, the rest say it says "Error_js5_connect" for them.
Any ideas?

item.title: How do I make a client work?
item.dc:creator: @legend-scape legend-scape
item.description:
@legend-scape wrote:

Error_js5_connect

Means your server is offline.
